Concatenate -

myName = input("What's youe girlfriend name? ")
myDoing = input("What is she doing now? ")
print(myName, "is a whore. Hence,", myDoing, "is what she does for survival!")


name = input("What is your name? ")
enemy = input ("What is your worst enemy’s name? ")
power = input ("What is your superpower? ")
live = input ("Where do you live? ")
food = input("What is your favorite food? ")
print()
print("Hello", name,"!. In order to overcome your worst enemy", enemy, "you need to use", power, "as your superpower. Living in", live, "you must be brave. Rest apart lets go have", food, "for dinner.")

